snippet.title: PewDiePie's Paradise Island - Outerminds' entry in Indies vs PewDiePie Game Jam
snippet.description:
I wrote the music for Outerminds' game jam game - you can vote on it here: http://jams.gamejolt.io/indiesvspewdiepie/games/pewdiepie-s-paradise-island/38934 - click "View Game" on the right to play it.

This game seems pretty simple - survive until the helicopter gets here, then make it to the choppa! But put it on "Bro" difficulty and the insanity really ramps up.
